---
import IndicatorLayout from '../../layouts/IndicatorLayout.astro';

const indicatorId = 'aroon';
const indicatorName = 'Aroon Indicator';
const description = `The Aroon Indicator is a technical analysis tool that measures the time between highs and lows over a given period. Developed by Tushar Chande in 1995, it consists of two lines (Aroon Up and Aroon Down) that help identify trend changes, trend strength, and potential consolidation periods.`;
const parameters = [
  {
    "name": "period",
    "type": "number",
    "default": 25,
    "min": 10,
    "max": 100,
    "description": "Number of periods to look back for highs and lows"
  }
];
---

<IndicatorLayout
  indicatorId={indicatorId}
  indicatorName={indicatorName}
  description={description}
  parameters={parameters}
>
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    The Aroon Indicator, developed by Tushar Chande in 1995, is a unique technical analysis tool that measures the time 
    elapsed since the most recent high and low within a given period. Named after the Sanskrit word for "dawn's early light," 
    the indicator is designed to reveal the beginning of a new trend.
  </p>
  <p>
    Unlike most indicators that focus on price or volume, Aroon focuses on time, making it particularly useful for 
    identifying when a trend is likely to begin or end. The indicator consists of two lines: Aroon Up (measuring time 
    since the last high) and Aroon Down (measuring time since the last low), both oscillating between 0 and 100.
  </p>

  <h2>How It Works</h2>
  <p>The Aroon Indicator calculates two separate lines:</p>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Aroon Up:</strong> Measures how long ago (in periods) the highest high occurred</li>
    <li><strong>Aroon Down:</strong> Measures how long ago (in periods) the lowest low occurred</li>
  </ol>
  
  <div class="not-prose bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg my-4 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
    <p class="font-mono text-sm mb-0 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
      Aroon Up = ((Period - Periods Since Highest High) / Period) × 100<br/>
      <br/>
      Aroon Down = ((Period - Periods Since Lowest Low) / Period) × 100<br/>
      <br/>
      Where:<br/>
      - Period = Lookback period (typically 25)<br/>
      - Values range from 0 to 100
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Time-Based:</strong> Measures time elapsed rather than price movement</li>
    <li><strong>Dual Lines:</strong> Separate indicators for uptrend and downtrend strength</li>
    <li><strong>Bounded Oscillator:</strong> Values always between 0 and 100</li>
    <li><strong>Early Trend Detection:</strong> Designed to identify trend changes early</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Interpretation & Trading Signals</h2>
  
  <h3>Value Interpretation</h3>
  <div class="not-prose bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-950/30 p-4 rounded-lg my-4 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800">
    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-lg text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100">Aroon Values:</h4>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"&gt;70-100:</strong> Strong trend in that direction</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"&gt;50-70:</strong> Trending market</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"&gt;30-50:</strong> Consolidating or weak trend</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"&gt;0-30:</strong> Trend weakness or reversal potential</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-lg text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100">Key Signals:</h4>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Aroon Up &gt; 70 & Aroon Down &lt; 30:</strong> Strong uptrend</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Aroon Down &gt; 70 & Aroon Up &lt; 30:</strong> Strong downtrend</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Both lines below 50:</strong> Consolidation phase</li>
      <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Crossovers:</strong> Potential trend changes</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3>Trading Strategies</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Trend Confirmation:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Buy when Aroon Up crosses above 50 while Aroon Down is below 50</li>
        <li>Sell when Aroon Down crosses above 50 while Aroon Up is below 50</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Extreme Readings:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Aroon Up at 100: New high just occurred, strong uptrend</li>
        <li>Aroon Down at 100: New low just occurred, strong downtrend</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Crossover Signals:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Bullish: Aroon Up crosses above Aroon Down</li>
        <li>Bearish: Aroon Down crosses above Aroon Up</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Consolidation Identification:</strong> Both lines between 0-50 indicate ranging market</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Advanced Interpretation</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Parallel Movement:</strong> When both lines move together, indicates strong trending behavior</li>
    <li><strong>Three-Phase System:</strong>
      <ol>
        <li>Aroon Up/Down reaches 100 (new trend emerging)</li>
        <li>Stays above 70 (trend confirmation)</li>
        <li>Falls below 50 (trend weakening)</li>
      </ol>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Divergence:</strong> Price making new highs/lows while Aroon fails to reach 100</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Practical Application</h2>
  
  <h3>Strengths</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Unique time-based approach provides different perspective</li>
    <li>Clear signals for trend strength and direction</li>
    <li>Excellent for identifying consolidation periods</li>
    <li>Works well in trending markets</li>
    <li>Simple to interpret with bounded values</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Limitations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Can give false signals in choppy markets</li>
    <li>Lagging indicator by nature</li>
    <li>Less effective in ranging markets with no clear highs/lows</li>
    <li>Period selection significantly affects signals</li>
    <li>Should be combined with other indicators for confirmation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Combination with Other Indicators</h2>
  <p>The Aroon Indicator works well when combined with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>ADX:</strong> Aroon for direction, ADX for trend strength confirmation</li>
    <li><strong>Moving Averages:</strong> Use Aroon to time MA crossover trades</li>
    <li><strong>Support/Resistance:</strong> Aroon signals more reliable near key levels</li>
    <li><strong>Volume Indicators:</strong> Confirm Aroon signals with volume</li>
    <li><strong>Oscillators (RSI, Stochastic):</strong> For additional entry/exit timing</li>
  </ul>

